Httrack - tool to clone auth pages
Source: https://www.httrack.com/

Usage:
  tool [commands] [options]

Example Usage:
  httrack --skeleton https://nostarch.com/user/

Options:
  --mirror       creates almost identical copy of the website
  --update       updates copy of existing website
  --continue     continues creating mirror copy of a website, if the process was interrupted or stopped
  --skeleton     copies only HTML files of the website
  -O            Output file

Informational:
  The bigger website the longer it takes to mirror it using -mirror flag and its easier to catch and block by a company, but it's more solid.
  If you don't care about obstructiveness of the website, use --skeleton flag.